{"word":"προεργάζομαι","slug":"προεργάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προεργάζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> with <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>άσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-είργασμαι</el>) </el><p/><i>to do</i> or <i>work at beforehand</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> also in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <el>τὰ προειργασμένα</el> <i>former deeds</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>ἡ προειργασμένη δόξα</el> glory <i>won before</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}